  1a &nbsp;Demonstrating Knowledge of Content and Pedagogy</b>

  <br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#149; Content knowledge &#149; Prerequisite relationships &#149; Content pedagogy

