  <br/><br/><b>

  3a &nbsp;Communicating with Students</b>

  <br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#149; Expectations for learning &#149; Directions, procedures, instruction drew students attention to relevant stimuli

